719:- The repo keeps compact progress/run-summary evidence in-repo, while raw per-attempt logs intentionally live outside the repo under `/Users/as/.areasong/task-loop-logs/AreaSong-Suite/<run_id>/...` [Task 2][Task 3]
726:- Symptom: long live smoke appears broken after a timeout with Cloudflare/403 chatter. Cause: child `codex exec` / external service noise, not necessarily repo logic. Fix: inspect logs and worktree after timeout before blaming the task-loop implementation [Task 2]
729:- Symptom: a slice shows `verify_result: pass` but the task-loop still marks it failed. Cause: the real failure is `git_checkpoint_status=git_diff_check_failed` during checkpoint scope validation, not verify. Fix: inspect `verify_result` and `git_checkpoint_status` separately before concluding the task itself failed [Task 4]
775:- The task-loop runner is still relevant to this slice family: copy-ready runs first, verify-ready second, verify FAIL retries the same unit, PASS is required before checkpoint, and git checkpoint rejects scope drift / outside-path changes [Task 1]
