   179	
   180	### 模块组织
   181	
   182	```
   183	AreaMatrix/
   184	├── App/        # AreaMatrixApp.swift, AppDelegate.swift
   185	├── Models/     # @Observable stores
   186	├── Bridge/     # CoreBridge, AppError, generated bindings
