    19	Completion evidence must name what changed, why it changed, which commands ran, whether those results are fresh after the final change, which checks did not run and why, remaining risks, and review / security / dependency / CI / Git evidence blocker state. Old logs, prior memories, dry-runs, screenshots, mock-only paths, fixture-only paths, hardcoded success, and agent self-reports are not completion evidence.
