  2729	### `preview_batch_delete(repoPath, fileIds, deleteMode) throws -> BatchDeletePreviewReport`
  2730	
  2731	```swift
  2732	let preview = try AreaMatrix.previewBatchDelete(
  2733	    repoPath: repoPath,
  2734	    fileIds: selectedFileIds,
  2735	    deleteMode: .moveToTrash
  2736	)
  2737	moveButton.isEnabled = preview.canApply
  2738	```
  2739	
  2740	C2-09 的只读批量删除预览入口，服务 `S2-13 batch-delete-confirm`。输入是已初始化
  2741	`repoPath`、多选得到的 `fileIds` 和 `deleteMode`。Stage 2 只允许两种模式：
  2742	
  2743	- `MoveToTrash`：计划把 AreaMatrix repo-owned 的 `Copied` / `Moved` 文件移到系统 Trash。
  2744	- `RemoveFromIndex`：计划只移除 Indexed / Adopted / External 或 Missing metadata 记录。
