  2976	### `correct_file_category(repoPath, fileId, category, moveFile, remember) throws -> ClassifierCorrectionResult`
  2977	
  2978	```swift
  2979	let result = try AreaMatrix.correctFileCategory(
  2980	    repoPath: repoPath,
  2981	    fileId: entry.id,
  2982	    category: "finance",
