  3862	## note API
  3863	
  3864	### `read_note(repoPath, fileId) throws -> String?`
  3865	
  3866	```swift
  3867	if let note = try AreaMatrix.readNote(repoPath: repoPath, fileId: entry.id) {
  3868	    detailView.noteEditor.text = note
  3869	}
  3870	```
  3871	
  3872	无笔记时返回 `nil`。
  3873	
  3874	### `write_note(repoPath, fileId, contentMd) throws`
  3875	
  3876	```swift
  3877	@MainActor
  3878	func saveNote(_ entry: FileEntry, content: String) async {
  3879	    let inflightPath = "\(entry.path).md"
  3880	    await inflightTracker.mark(inflightPath)
  3881	    defer { Task { await inflightTracker.unmark(inflightPath) } }
  3882	
  3883	    do {
  3884	        try await Task.detached {
  3885	            try AreaMatrix.writeNote(
  3886	                repoPath: repoPath,
  3887	                fileId: entry.id,
  3888	                contentMd: content
  3889	            )
  3890	        }.value
  3891	    } catch {
  3892	        await showAlert("保存笔记失败：\(error.localizedDescription)")
  3893	    }
  3894	}
  3895	```
  3896	
  3897	应用同时写：
  3898	
  3899	- DB `notes` 表
  3900	- 物理文件 `<filename>.md`（与文件同目录）
  3901	
  3902	`InFlightTracker` 标记避免 watcher 把这次写视为外部变化（详见 [../architecture/fs-watcher.md](../architecture/fs-watcher.md)）。
  3903	
